                <p dir="ltr">A small update has arrived to <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/call-of-duty-warzone/" data-ref-id="5000-572198">Call of Duty: Warzone</a> on December 19, which introduces the new Archie's Festival Frenzy event. The patch notes detail audio improvements and bug fixes for battle royale, as well as the arrival of the season's new sniper rifle.</p><p dir="ltr">Season 1 Reloaded adds the brand-new AMR Mod 4 sniper rifle, which can be earned for free in both Black Ops 6 and Warzone as a reward in the Archie's Festival Frenzy event. As previously <a href="https://x.com/charlieINTEL/status/1869795007743570362" rel="nofollow ">reported by CharlieIntel</a>, the weapon is also already available for purchase as a store bundle.</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="2029428175" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6465481,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;COD%20Warzone%20%26%20Black%20Ops%206%20-%20Season%2001%20Battle%20Pass%20Overview%20Trailer&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:69,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/cod-warzone-black-ops-6-season-01-battle-pass-overview-trailer\/2300-6465481\/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465481\/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465481\/\&quot; height=\&quot;360\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;,&quot;480&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6465481\/\&quot; height=\&quot;270\&quot; width=\&quot;480\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;}},&quot;device&quot;:&quot;other&quot;,&quot;is