data-width="100%" data-height="100%" data-video-start="0"><div><p>COD Warzone &amp; Black Ops 6 - Season 01 Battle Pass Overview Trailer</p><div><p>         Want us to remember this setting for all your devices?       </p><p><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/signup/">Sign up</a> or <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/login/">Sign in</a> now!       </p></div></div><p>       Please use a html5 video capable browser to watch videos.     </p><p>       This video has an invalid file format.     </p><p>Sorry, but you can't access this content!</p></div><p dir="ltr">In addition to the new weapon, the patch notes reveal a few adjustments to improve footstep audio. This includes an increase in volume for enemy footsteps, while decreasing the volume of first-person player footsteps. It also reduces the environmental reverb effects across all players, including teammate and enemy footsteps.</p><p dir="ltr">The update makes a few changes to the game's weapon restrictions. The CHF Barrel attachment is blocked on the new AMR Mod 4 sniper rifle, but the attachment is no longer restricted from the COR 45 pistol or the akimbo variant of the Saug submachine gun.</p><p dir="ltr">For bug fixes, the update corrects an issue in the Holiday Rush mode that prevented Santa from aiming at lower elevations. An exploit is also patched that previously allowed players to use unintended perks.</p><p>The full patch notes for Warzone can be seen below, as <a href="https://www.callofduty.com/patchnotes/2024/11/call-of-duty-bo6-warzone-season-01-patch-notes" rel="nofollow ">shared by Activision</a>.</p><p>Activision recently revealed an <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/call-of-duty-teases-squid-game-collab-for-black-ops-6-and-warzone/1100-6528158/">upcoming Squid Game collaboration</a> for January, and another upcoming Call of Duty shop bundle includes a <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/cods-newest-finisher-is-the-most-absurd-one-yet-and-thats-saying-something/1100-6528479/" data-ref-id="1100-6528479">deadly unicorn finishing move</a>.</p><h2>WARZONE WEAPONS</h2><ul><li>The AMR Mod 4 Sniper Rifle is now available.</li></ul><ul><li>Restricted the AMR Mod 4 CHF Barrel Attachment.</li></ul><ul><li>Removed restriction on COR 45 Pistol.</li></ul><ul><li>Removed restriction on Saug Akimbo Attachment.</li></ul><h2>AUDIO</h2><ul><li>Reduced environmental reverb effects across all player, friendly and enemy footsteps.</li></ul><ul><li>Reduced volume of first-person player footsteps.</li></ul><ul><li>Increased volume of enemy footsteps.</li></ul><h2>BUG FIXES</h2><ul><li>Fixed an exploit that allowed players to use unintended Perks.  <ul><li>We are continuing to investigate an unrelated issue with the Ghost Perk.</li></ul></li></ul><ul><li>Fixed collision issues with various elements across Urzikstan allowing Players to exploit/peek/shoot through them.</li></ul><ul><li>Fixed an issue in Holiday Rush where Santa was unable to aim at lower elevations.</li></ul>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
